               <p>I am a constable: as I was going by Mr. Johnson's I saw a great mob; I went to assist Mr. Johnson; the prisoner said, as he had only taken the watch off the hook and not out of the house, it was but a misdemeanor; and he could only be imprisoned six months.</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I am innocent of the charge.</p>
